1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 25=

3
00:00:17,839 --> 00:00:18,480
My dear.

4
00:00:19,540 --> 00:00:21,000
We've led the pursuers away for now.

5
00:00:21,359 --> 00:00:22,000
However,

6
00:00:22,440 --> 00:00:24,160
they are bound to put a price
on our heads.

7
00:00:24,679 --> 00:00:25,679
For the time being,

8
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:27,320
we need to stay out of sight.

9
00:00:27,737 --> 00:00:28,912
We need to find

10
00:00:28,912 --> 00:00:30,432
a safe place to lie low.

11
00:00:31,160 --> 00:00:32,719
I know of a safe hideout.

12
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:55,679
Move, move, move!

13
00:01:05,359 --> 00:01:06,519
Do you think it's safe here?

14
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:09,450
Sometimes, the most dangerous place
is the safest.

15
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:10,760
Luo Wushuang would never guess

16
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:12,000
that we'd come back.

17
00:01:16,239 --> 00:01:17,120
Did you hear?

18
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:18,319
Chief Mao's fiancée

19
00:01:18,319 --> 00:01:19,200
is a villain.

20
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,760
She's in league with the Jade Squirrel.

21
00:01:20,760 --> 00:01:21,560
What a mess.

22
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:22,480
- Really?
- I never would've thought!

23
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,319
You really can't tell.

24
00:01:23,319 --> 00:01:24,079
That's him, right?

25
00:01:24,079 --> 00:01:24,680
Unbelievable.

26
00:01:30,260 --> 00:01:30,963
Let's move along.

27
00:02:06,599 --> 00:02:07,239
Yu.

28
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:11,439
Vice Minister Zhou wants to see you.

29
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:23,199
Your fiancée is the Jade Squirrel.

30
00:02:23,919 --> 00:02:24,879
Care to explain?

31
00:02:25,110 --> 00:02:26,280
Why should I have to explain?

32
00:02:27,199 --> 00:02:27,960
Impudent!

33
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,400
As the Deputy of the Arrest Corps,

34
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:33,319
your wife is from the Martial World,

35
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,360
and the leader of the Sacred Hand Sect.

36
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,960
And you ask why I demand an explanation?

37
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:39,400
I have nothing to say on the matter.

38
00:02:39,400 --> 00:02:39,960
Yu,

39
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,439
watch your tone.

40
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:42,680
Fine.

41
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:43,840
Tell me,

42
00:02:44,479 --> 00:02:47,120
did you know that Chu Yunchang

43
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:48,520
was the Jade Squirrel all along?

44
00:02:49,439 --> 00:02:50,520
Tell me, Vice Minister,

45
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:53,360
exactly what evil
has the Jade Squirrel done?

46
00:02:54,319 --> 00:02:54,919
She...

47
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:00,680
She is a member of the Martial World!

48
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:03,879
The Martial World?

49
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:08,080
Many in the Gate Bureau
come from that world.

50
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:10,199
Are they all guilty too?

51
00:03:10,439 --> 00:03:10,960
You...

52
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:14,289
They left to serve the Imperial Court.

53
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,879
If Chu Yunchang did the same,

54
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,639
would her past be forgiven?

55
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,759
She is different.

56
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,960
How so?

57
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,719
Chu Yunchang...

58
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,199
What about her?

59
00:03:29,039 --> 00:03:31,290
Repeatedly sneaking
into the Gate Bureau to cause trouble

60
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:33,159
and obstructing official business.

61
00:03:34,210 --> 00:03:35,199
Those are serious crimes.

62
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:37,800
Exactly.

63
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:40,599
She's self-righteous
and has no respect for the law.

64
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:43,520
Her grandfather even lost
the Sacred Token.

65
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,319
What is her goal in doing all this?

66
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:47,240
To defy the Imperial Court.

67
00:03:48,199 --> 00:03:49,080
For all these years,

68
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:52,360
Chu Yunchang has been searching
for that Sacred Token

69
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:54,159
to disband the Sacred Hand Sect.

70
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,240
She has never used
her status as Sect Leader

71
00:03:57,599 --> 00:03:59,039
to commit a single illegal act.

72
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:01,759
Mao Buyu!

73
00:04:01,879 --> 00:04:03,080
Time and time again,

74
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:05,000
you speak up for this Jade Squirrel

75
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,319
just to defy me.

76
00:04:06,919 --> 00:04:08,039
What is the meaning of this?

77
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,479
Please calm yourself, Vice Minister.

78
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:14,919
Mao Buyu was deceived
by the Jade Squirrel.

79
00:04:15,600 --> 00:04:17,519
It's only natural he feels lost
and responsible.

80
00:04:17,759 --> 00:04:19,240
That is why he is lashing out

81
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,600
with these extreme words.

82
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:23,680
I hope

83
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:27,439
you can show some leniency.

84
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,079
I'm not feeling self-reproach,

85
00:04:29,475 --> 00:04:30,554
and I'm perfectly calm.

86
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:32,680
I just don't get it.

87
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:34,560
Isn't the Gate Bureau

88
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,000
supposed to rely on evidence?

89
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:37,639
For years now,

90
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:41,150
the Sacred Hand Sect has vanished
without committing a single major crime.

91
00:04:41,879 --> 00:04:43,800
Why are you all so hostile toward her?

92
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:47,879
Chu Yunchang has always
used her influence

93
00:04:47,879 --> 00:04:48,759
to restrain her sect

94
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,680
from breaking the laws.

95
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:53,360
Yet, you refuse to accept her.

96
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,759
Even if she is the Jade Squirrel,

97
00:04:58,639 --> 00:05:00,000
you still need hard evidence

98
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:01,079
of some heinous crime

99
00:05:01,079 --> 00:05:02,319
before you can arrest her!

100
00:05:02,319 --> 00:05:03,480
- So you're saying...
- You!

101
00:05:04,079 --> 00:05:04,839
Mao Buyu!

102
00:05:05,199 --> 00:05:07,759
Are you accusing the Gate Bureau
of framing people?

103
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:09,759
I wouldn't dare.

104
00:05:10,519 --> 00:05:12,120
But I ask the Commissioner to clarify.

105
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:15,040
What illegal act
has Chu Yunchang committed?

106
00:05:15,380 --> 00:05:17,625
Breaking into the Gate Bureau
and sneaking into my study

107
00:05:17,625 --> 00:05:18,480
with ill intent.

108
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,959
That is ironclad evidence!

109
00:05:19,959 --> 00:05:21,240
But Commissioner,

110
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:24,480
why was Dongfang Qing,
the Thousand-Hand Titan,

111
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,160
also in your room that very night?

112
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:26,959
You...

113
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,879
What deal was being made

114
00:05:29,879 --> 00:05:31,160
between Dongfang Qing and you?

115
00:05:34,450 --> 00:05:37,051
And did Dongfang Qing really die
at the hands of Chu Yunchang?

116
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,600
Impudence!

117
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:41,600
Is that any way to speak
to your superior?

118
00:05:43,060 --> 00:05:45,079
The Sacred Hand Sect
has always been a wicked cult.

119
00:05:45,399 --> 00:05:46,759
After losing the Sacred Token,

120
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:49,240
the Imperial Court has
revoke its recognition.

121
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,839
As the Sect Leader,
Chu Yunchang's squabble

122
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:53,680
with Dongfang Qing is just dog-eat-dog.

123
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:56,519
It's clear she has ulterior motives.

124
00:05:57,319 --> 00:05:59,079
Then, why didn't the Imperial Court

125
00:05:59,530 --> 00:06:01,120
ban the sect when it was first founded?

126
00:06:02,020 --> 00:06:04,040
But the moment Chu Zhongtian
lost the Sacred Token,

127
00:06:04,439 --> 00:06:05,680
the Imperial Court began

128
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,350
suppressing them
with everything they had.

129
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,079
Is it not true

130
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:12,319
that the Sacred Hand Sect once
collaborated with the Gate Bureau?

131
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,680
What exactly happened

132
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:17,839
to make the Imperial Court suddenly
brand them as a wicked cult?

133
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,000
Mao Buyu,

134
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,439
how dare you!

135
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:24,519
You shield a common thief at every turn,

136
00:06:24,959 --> 00:06:27,040
defend the Jade Squirrel
at every opportunity,

137
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:28,399
and disparage the Imperial Court.

138
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:31,240
If not for your past achievements,

139
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:33,120
I would throw you in the dungeon now!

140
00:06:33,759 --> 00:06:34,560
Commissioner,

141
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,240
have mercy.

142
00:06:41,879 --> 00:06:42,920
As of today,

143
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,160
Mao Buyu is suspended from duty

144
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,920
pending further investigation.

145
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:06,399
I thank you for the leniency.

146
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:12,759
Yu...

147
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:15,920
Yu!

148
00:07:16,879 --> 00:07:17,639
Mao Buyu!

149
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:18,480
This...

150
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:22,040
Go find a place to rest for now.

151
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:23,839
What about you?

152
00:07:23,839 --> 00:07:25,370
I'll head into the city to gather intel

153
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:28,040
and see how the Gate Bureau
plans to move against us.

154
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:29,279
Uncle,

155
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,399
I'll go with you.

156
00:07:30,639 --> 00:07:31,240
No.

157
00:07:31,650 --> 00:07:32,639
It's been a long night.

158
00:07:32,639 --> 00:07:33,480
Get some rest.

159
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:36,839
What?

160
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:39,480
Are you actually worried about me?

161
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:41,759
My dear,

162
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:44,920
please be careful.

163
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:53,959
Kneel.

164
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,399
Why?

165
00:07:58,850 --> 00:08:00,120
You defied our family teaching.

166
00:08:03,210 --> 00:08:04,720
What did I do to violate our teaching?

167
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:07,160
Why did you lash out
at the Commissioner?

168
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,240
Why were you defending
the Sacred Hand Sect?

169
00:08:10,519 --> 00:08:11,079
Father,

170
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,600
I can't let the Gate Bureau
lay down the law.

171
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:15,240
As a constable,

172
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:16,240
I should uphold the law,

173
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:17,480
not using it to settle scores.

174
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:20,170
The Sacred Hand Sect may
belong to the Martial World,

175
00:08:20,180 --> 00:08:21,990
but they haven't
committed any crimes in years.

176
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,880
Just because they are part
of the Martial World,

177
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:25,250
you blindly treat them

178
00:08:25,250 --> 00:08:26,399
as outcasts.

179
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,040
How is that fair?

180
00:08:28,812 --> 00:08:29,572
How dare you!

181
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:32,759
How dare you speak with such insolence?

182
00:08:34,519 --> 00:08:35,440
If I don't speak up,

183
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,679
no one will.

184
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:39,680
You're being insubordinate
and you think you're in the right?

185
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:41,039
If a superior is unjust,

186
00:08:41,050 --> 00:08:42,639
why can't a subordinate speak the truth?

187
00:08:42,639 --> 00:08:44,279
Are you trying to be the death of me?

188
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:46,360
Our family has served
the Gate Bureau for generations.

189
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:48,480
We've only ever focused
on solving cases.

190
00:08:48,480 --> 00:08:51,159
Never has anyone questioned
a superior's decision like you!

191
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:52,399
That's why we are in decline.

192
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:53,600
We've become a laughingstock!

193
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,519
Outrageous!

194
00:08:54,759 --> 00:08:56,039
Father, what are you doing?

195
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:56,799
Stay out of this!

196
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,600
Grandfather.

197
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:09,879
Zhou has left, I assume?

198
00:09:11,559 --> 00:09:12,279
Hand it over.

199
00:09:17,275 --> 00:09:18,120
(Token)

200
00:09:18,120 --> 00:09:20,200
(Chu's Residence)
My men searched the Chu's Residence last night.

201
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:22,120
(They found)

202
00:09:22,290 --> 00:09:24,000
(the silver Sacred Token
in a secret room.)

203
00:09:30,879 --> 00:09:32,279
So it turns out the Sacred Token

204
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:35,200
was in the hands
of the Chu family all along.

205
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,759
The Sacred Token...

206
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:40,279
After all these years,

207
00:09:40,399 --> 00:09:43,000
you certainly made me work for it.

208
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:46,720
(Token)
Grandfather,

209
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,200
why didn't you hand the Sacred Token

210
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,399
over to the Vice Minister?

211
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,120
That fool?

212
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:55,399
That would be
a waste of such a treasure.

213
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,639
Do you realize that this single token

214
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:59,279
can make the whole Martial World bow?

215
00:09:59,679 --> 00:10:01,960
And if both tokens were combined,

216
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:04,240
one could command all the sects.

217
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,919
I understand now.

218
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,759
You plan to use the Sacred Token

219
00:10:08,960 --> 00:10:11,279
to wipe out all the sects
in one fell swoop.

220
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:15,279
If that were the case,

221
00:10:15,660 --> 00:10:18,000
what use would the Imperial Court
have for the Gate Bureau?

222
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,080
Then, what is your plan?

223
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:25,120
I'm going to use the Sacred Token

224
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:27,519
to ensure the Martial World
never knows peace.

225
00:10:31,879 --> 00:10:32,879
I don't follow.

226
00:10:35,519 --> 00:10:36,720
The more chaotic it becomes,

227
00:10:37,279 --> 00:10:41,399
the more the Imperial Court
will rely on the Gate Bureau.

228
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:45,519
Brilliant, Grandfather.

229
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:47,600
Who's there?

230
00:11:00,759 --> 00:11:02,320
You're both acting on impulse

231
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:03,700
without knowing the consequences.

232
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,960
Nowadays, the Gate Bureau

233
00:11:05,279 --> 00:11:06,759
is run entirely by the Luo family.

234
00:11:06,759 --> 00:11:08,440
Do you have any idea how ruthless

235
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,519
Commissioner Luo is?

236
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,360
He has singlehandedly

237
00:11:12,740 --> 00:11:14,759
controlled the Gate Bureau
for over twenty years.

238
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:16,919
Do you truly believe he is

239
00:11:16,919 --> 00:11:19,080
some old man who only drinks tea?

240
00:11:21,159 --> 00:11:22,710
If our family ever wants to rise again,

241
00:11:23,039 --> 00:11:24,840
if we want to restore
the glory of this house,

242
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,799
we have no choice but to
swallow our pride

243
00:11:26,799 --> 00:11:28,799
and dance to the tune of others.

244
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,320
You broke your engagement to Wushuang

245
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,399
and offended Luo Shixun.

246
00:11:31,679 --> 00:11:33,240
He could ruin your future

247
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:35,039
with a single snap of his fingers!

248
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:35,759
Father...

249
00:11:36,639 --> 00:11:38,320
Beat me or curse me if you must,

250
00:11:38,620 --> 00:11:41,000
but I will never betray my conscience
to play the sycophant.

251
00:11:41,519 --> 00:11:42,759
Buyu,

252
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,240
do you really want to see

253
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,559
our family's ancestral legacy

254
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:47,159
come to a dead end with you?

255
00:11:52,799 --> 00:11:53,639
Father-in-law,

256
00:11:54,650 --> 00:11:55,720
I'm afraid you're mistaken.

257
00:11:56,170 --> 00:11:57,159
What are you doing here?

258
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,600
My dear. Buyu.

259
00:12:00,087 --> 00:12:00,926
Father-in-law,

260
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:02,440
I have a question.

261
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:04,320
As the Chief of the Probe Corps,

262
00:12:04,679 --> 00:12:06,159
if you were to interrogate Yunchang,

263
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:09,080
on what grounds would you convict her?

264
00:12:14,519 --> 00:12:15,120
Well...

265
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,080
Rong,

266
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:20,639
your Intel Corps holds information
from across the land.

267
00:12:20,639 --> 00:12:24,159
Is there any ironclad evidence
of the Jade Squirrel's crimes?

268
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,080
Well,

269
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:27,440
there is none.

270
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:31,600
Years ago,

271
00:12:31,919 --> 00:12:35,360
to eliminate
the lawless Southern Thieves,

272
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,679
the Gate Bureau actually relied
on the Sacred Hand Sect.

273
00:12:38,559 --> 00:12:40,799
Since its founding, the Sacred Hand Sect

274
00:12:41,399 --> 00:12:43,679
has always kept its disciples
under strict restraint,

275
00:12:44,159 --> 00:12:46,440
and they cooperated
with the Imperial Court many times.

276
00:12:47,799 --> 00:12:49,759
However, at some point,

277
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:53,159
they were suddenly
branded as a wicked cult

278
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:56,320
and placed on the wanted list.

279
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:02,279
In recent years, Luo Shixun has ruled

280
00:13:02,279 --> 00:13:03,812
the Gate Bureau with an iron fist,

281
00:13:03,812 --> 00:13:04,790
manipulating everything.

282
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,799
He has built up his own faction.

283
00:13:07,440 --> 00:13:10,320
I have no idea what he is plotting.

284
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:14,919
Father-in-law,

285
00:13:15,480 --> 00:13:18,240
if Buyu were to blindly follow
and flatter him,

286
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:20,320
wouldn't he be
losing his sense of justice

287
00:13:20,410 --> 00:13:21,600
and violating our family code?

288
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:27,919
But now that we have
offended Luo Shixun,

289
00:13:29,039 --> 00:13:30,000
how will our family

290
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:33,720
maintain its standing
within the Gate Bureau?

291
00:13:34,279 --> 00:13:35,200
I beg to differ.

292
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:38,440
Luo Wushuang has always
been infatuated with Buyu.

293
00:13:38,780 --> 00:13:39,799
When it comes down to it,

294
00:13:40,080 --> 00:13:41,639
she will speak up on his behalf.

295
00:13:44,519 --> 00:13:45,200
Buyu,

296
00:13:45,759 --> 00:13:47,279
you are far too blunt.

297
00:13:47,639 --> 00:13:49,519
If you want to uncover the cause,

298
00:13:49,519 --> 00:13:50,600
to find the truth

299
00:13:50,799 --> 00:13:52,000
and trace it to its source,

300
00:13:53,279 --> 00:13:56,279
you must first ensure your own safety.

301
00:13:57,519 --> 00:13:58,399
Heed my advice.

302
00:13:58,399 --> 00:14:01,120
Reflect on your actions at home
these next few days.

303
00:14:01,279 --> 00:14:02,799
Don't go looking for trouble.

304
00:14:03,519 --> 00:14:07,120
I expect Luo Wushuang will
plead your case soon enough.

305
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:10,279
When she does, you'll likely
get off with a reprimand.

306
00:14:10,679 --> 00:14:13,279
As long as you can stay
within the Arrest Corps,

307
00:14:13,519 --> 00:14:16,080
you'll have a real chance

308
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:19,720
to get to the bottom
of this entire situation.

309
00:14:30,919 --> 00:14:33,360
We've all been exposed this time.

310
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,559
Our wanted posters are everywhere.

311
00:14:35,799 --> 00:14:36,879
Everywhere?

312
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:42,840
This is definitely a tricky situation.

313
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,480
It's my fault.

314
00:14:44,759 --> 00:14:45,960
I've dragged you all into this.

315
00:14:46,159 --> 00:14:47,360
How can you blame yourself?

316
00:14:48,725 --> 00:14:51,085
Being hunted by the authorities
is just a part of life

317
00:14:51,090 --> 00:14:52,547
for those of us in the Martial World.

318
00:14:53,559 --> 00:14:55,720
It's just a pity
that my silver Sacred Token

319
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:56,759
was left at the house.

320
00:14:57,399 --> 00:15:00,120
The Gate Bureau must have
seized it by now.

321
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:02,320
My father

322
00:15:02,559 --> 00:15:04,480
went through so much to find it.

323
00:15:05,159 --> 00:15:06,799
Now, I've gone and lost it again.

324
00:15:08,639 --> 00:15:10,000
I've truly failed my ancestors.

325
00:15:13,759 --> 00:15:15,600
Don't beat yourself up over it.

326
00:15:16,799 --> 00:15:18,600
Let's just take things
one step at a time.

327
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:24,679
I've had Jia Yizhen
for some new identities for us,

328
00:15:24,759 --> 00:15:25,919
just in case.

329
00:15:28,639 --> 00:15:30,200
Are we going to hide out in the South?

330
00:15:30,799 --> 00:15:32,120
The South might not even be safe.

331
00:15:33,039 --> 00:15:33,919
What I'm suggesting is

332
00:15:34,639 --> 00:15:35,600
that we head to Xichuan.

333
00:15:36,519 --> 00:15:39,159
But the road to Xichuan
is heavily guarded.

334
00:15:39,340 --> 00:15:41,519
Will these fake identities
get us past the checkpoints?

335
00:15:42,039 --> 00:15:43,159
One thing at a time.

336
00:15:46,039 --> 00:15:47,120
We can't stay here.

337
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:49,639
Let's leave tomorrow night.
What do you say?

338
00:15:51,159 --> 00:15:51,919
Tomorrow night...

339
00:15:59,279 --> 00:15:59,919
Chang.

340
00:16:00,320 --> 00:16:02,279
My mother gave this to me
before she passed.

341
00:16:02,279 --> 00:16:03,540
I've kept it with me ever since.

342
00:16:03,799 --> 00:16:06,399
She told me that
if I ever found the one I love,

343
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:08,279
I should give it to her.

344
00:16:11,862 --> 00:16:17,212
♪My heart's desire is tangled
by the chaos of this world♪

345
00:16:18,587 --> 00:16:23,487
♪While the gears of fate
keep turning on♪

346
00:16:23,639 --> 00:16:25,480
(This is a charm I got from the temple.)

347
00:16:26,919 --> 00:16:29,480
(You're out there fighting every day.)

348
00:16:30,360 --> 00:16:31,960
(It makes me so worried about you.)

349
00:16:32,312 --> 00:16:36,837
♪Obsessions linger on♪

350
00:16:36,919 --> 00:16:37,720
(What if...)

351
00:16:38,879 --> 00:16:40,720
(And this is purely hypothetical...)

352
00:16:41,879 --> 00:16:43,600
What if I really were the Jade Squirrel?

353
00:16:45,639 --> 00:16:46,919
What would you do then?

354
00:16:46,975 --> 00:16:51,087
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

355
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:51,840
I think...

356
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:55,440
you must have your own reasons for it.

357
00:16:56,559 --> 00:16:57,720
But would you arrest me?

358
00:16:58,159 --> 00:16:58,799
Yes.

359
00:16:59,799 --> 00:17:00,919
Because I am a constable.

360
00:17:08,799 --> 00:17:09,359
Who's there?

361
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:19,079
Chang?

362
00:17:19,839 --> 00:17:20,480
Chang!

363
00:17:50,475 --> 00:17:53,750
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

364
00:17:53,788 --> 00:17:56,663
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

365
00:17:57,163 --> 00:18:02,881
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

366
00:18:04,063 --> 00:18:07,383
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

367
00:18:07,513 --> 00:18:10,433
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

368
00:18:11,601 --> 00:18:16,841
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

369
00:18:18,063 --> 00:18:20,456
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

370
00:18:20,456 --> 00:18:24,106
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

371
00:18:24,175 --> 00:18:27,665
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

372
00:18:27,763 --> 00:18:30,738
♪To the ends of time♪

373
00:18:30,738 --> 00:18:34,113
♪The moon traces your face♪

374
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:37,888
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

375
00:18:37,888 --> 00:18:44,128
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

376
00:18:44,463 --> 00:18:47,678
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

377
00:18:47,963 --> 00:18:51,501
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

378
00:18:51,788 --> 00:18:54,813
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

379
00:18:54,813 --> 00:18:57,913
♪On our way to forever♪

380
00:18:57,913 --> 00:19:01,763
♪The moon traces your face♪

381
00:19:01,763 --> 00:19:05,123
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

382
00:19:05,313 --> 00:19:11,273
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

383
00:19:12,350 --> 00:19:21,990
♪Just to be with you♪
